*------------------------------( Misc: Butcher )-----------------------------*

   Type:        command
   Usage:       butcher <corpse>
                
   Description: Butcher some meat from a dead corpse. You need the skills
		fauna lore and the weapon skill to make a success. Good
		cooks get better meat then bad ones. Remember that you need
		a sharp weapon to butcher with.
                
   Example:     butcher corpse
   
*----------------------------------------------------------------------------*
See also: 'fauna lore', 'skills'